						<leaderTitleMale>Exochrome Chief</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Exochrome Chief</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>When the archotechs appeared they were never concerned for appearances; they showed us that the mind stands above the physical form. That was breeding with animals. In the future, when the archotechs withdraw to higher planes, we the faithful shall remain as eternal stewards of their herd, our wombs and theirs entwined in unending sacred cycle.</description>
