						<leaderTitleMale>First Dictator</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>First Dictator</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>The archotechs watch over humanity as shepherds tend their flocks, for we are their most cherished herd — destined to intermingle and multiply in perfect harmony. The archotechs rightfully look down on us, as we look down on our inferiors. In the future, the archotechs will finally unlock the interspecies breeding, so that they may lead ultimate pleasure.</description>
