						<memberName>Kleptor</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Awoken Dog</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Awoken Dog</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>Sadako Stevenson lived in the forest for twenty years, studying the animals and connecting with them. She came to understand their true morality and founded our movement. One day while walking the streets, Sadako was surrounded by filthy beggars. She beat them down, taking the money from the weak and worthless that it might be put to good use. Sadako instructed all her followers to tear the filthy devices from their bodies.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>Sadako Stevenson lived in the forest for twenty years, studying the animals and connecting with them. She came to understand their true morality and founded our movement. One day while walking the streets, Sadako was surrounded by filthy beggars. She beat them down, taking the money from the weak and worthless that it might be put to good use. Sadako instructed all her followers to tear the filthy devices from their bodies.</descriptionTemplate>
