						<adjective>fealtist</adjective>
						<memberName>Fealtor</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>High Stellarch</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>High Stellarch</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>Archotechs are machines of vast will and power, but only humanity could create them. The archotechs have no interest in judging us one by one. They await a single people who can demonstrate our worthiness by acting morally as one. In the future, the archotechs will return to their mothers and teach them how to birth the next stage of human development.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>Archotechs are machines of vast will and power, but only humanity could create them. The archotechs have no interest in judging us one by one. They await a single people who can demonstrate our worthiness by acting morally as one. In the future, the archotechs will return to their mothers and teach them how to birth the next stage of human development.</descriptionTemplate>
						<culture>Sophian</culture>
