						<name>Yttaki Creed</name>
						<adjective>animist</adjective>
						<memberName>Animist</memberName>
						<leaderTitleMale>Great Curate</leaderTitleMale>
						<leaderTitleFemale>Great Curate</leaderTitleFemale>
						<description>The universe is an endless cycle of creation and destruction managed by spirits in aspects of the world around us. To cover our bodies with cloth is to hide the nature of the spirits within us, and it makes them restless. Our sages say that a powerful spirit of destruction will end the universe, but that a woman will wield the spirit of the &lt;color=#D09B61FF&gt;Skin-Remembrance&lt;/color&gt; recreate the universe anew.</description>
						<descriptionTemplate>The universe is an endless cycle of creation and destruction managed by spirits in aspects of the world around us. To cover our bodies with cloth is to hide the nature of the spirits within us, and it makes them restless. Our sages say that a powerful spirit of destruction will end the universe, but that a woman will wield the spirit of the %%relic0_name%% recreate the universe anew.</descriptionTemplate>
